<definition-item date-revised="2016-11-01"><classification-symbol scheme="cpc">C10H</classification-symbol><definition-title>PRODUCTION OF ACETYLENE BY WET METHODS {(purification of acetylene <class-ref scheme="cpc">C07C7/00</class-ref>)}</definition-title><definition-statement>
      <section-title>Definition statement</section-title>
      <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
        <paragraph-text type="body">Methods and apparatus for production of acetylene by wet methods, including arrangements for water feed and carbide feed; high-pressure acetylene generators; details of acetylene generators, e.g. carbide cartridges, carbide compositions, safety devices, sludge removal.</paragraph-text>
      </section-body>
